  "contentHtml": "\n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>New Delhi: <a href=\"/tag/marengo+asia+hospitals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Marengo Asia Hospitals</a> Faridabad, has launched a tele-proctor <a href=\"/tag/robotic+surgery+program\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">robotic surgery program</a> to improve access to robotic <a href=\"/tag/knee+replacement+surgery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">knee replacement surgery</a> in tier 2 and tier 3 cities.According to the hospital, “tele-proctoring utilises advanced telecommunication technology integrated with fully automated robotic systems like MISSO, enabling real-time surgical guidance, secure connectivity, and enhanced precision which allows expert surgeons to remotely monitor and support procedures with exceptional accuracy.”</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Under the program, the hospital successfully carried out tele-proctor robotic knee replacement surgery of a 67-year-old woman, with real-time remote guidance from Dr. Anurag Aggarwal, Clinical Director and Head - Orthopaedics &amp; Robotic Joint Replacement, Marengo Asia Hospitals.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>“Today <a href=\"/tag/tele-proctoring\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">tele-proctoring</a> is bridging the gap between technical training and real-world surgical mastery by directing surgeons through live procedures under the supervision of experienced robotic experts. During robotic knee replacement procedures, it significantly improves surgeon confidence, procedural accuracy, and overall patient experience,\" Aggarwal added.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Jun 19, 2026 at 05:10 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Jun 19, 2026 at 05:10 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights 